<plot>'INDISCRETION' is a harrowing morality tale of past sins exposed and old wounds reopened. An abused 12 yr old girl writes a note to God, tying it to a balloon. It becomes the catalyst that will connect the troubled lives of others when it causes a fatal car accident. Gabriel, a paramedic who carries his own torment over the loss of his son, finds the note at the scene of the accident. The note ultimately ends up in the reluctant hands of a priest, Lionel, who has been repressing his own demons from his childhood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?264514</url></doc>
